    "Title": "[AI 摘要] 聯發科以高階主管到職發展計畫，再奪國際人才發展協會卓越實務獎",
    "Content": "聯發科 (2454) 今日宣布，以「高階主管到職發展計畫」再度榮獲國際人才發展協會 (ATD) 卓越實務獎，股價今日收盤為 3155.00 元，下跌 245.00 元，跌幅 -7.21%。\n\n聯發科繼去年獲獎後，今年再次以該計畫脫穎而出，該計畫自 2020 年執行至今，已協助超過百位主管快速融入團隊並激發協作綜效，有助於公司進入新市場與技術突破。\n\n資料來源：新聞庫 | 期間：過去 48 小時\n\nIC設計龍頭聯發科 (2454) 今日宣布，以「高階主管到職發展計畫」(Executive Onboarding Program)，再度榮獲全球人才發展領域「奧斯卡獎」之稱的國際人才發展協會 (Association For Talent Development, ATD) 卓越實務獎  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E4%BA%8C%E5%BA%A6%E5%A5%AA%E7%8D%8E-%E6%8B%BF%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95atd%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%8D%8E-084208004.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E4%BB%A5%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0%E8%81%B7%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%86%8D%E5%A5%AAatd%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E5%AF%A6%E5%8B%99%E7%8D%8E-080200073.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[2]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0%E8%81%B7%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%86%8D%E5%A5%AA%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E5%AF%A6%E5%8B%99%E7%8D%8E-072936217.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0%E8%81%B7%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E7%8D%B2%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E7%8D%8E-070804037.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[4]</a>。聯發科表示，該計畫透過系統化方式，協助新任主管快速發揮價值，進而達成組織營運目標  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E4%BA%8C%E5%BA%A6%E5%A5%AA%E7%8D%8E-%E6%8B%BF%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95atd%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%8D%8E-084208004.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E4%BB%A5%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0%E8%81%B7%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%86%8D%E5%A5%AAatd%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E5%AF%A6%E5%8B%99%E7%8D%8E-080200073.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[2]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0%E8%81%B7%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%86%8D%E5%A5%AA%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E5%AF%A6%E5%8B%99%E7%8D%8E-072936217.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a>。聯發科資深副總經理暨人資長林秀瑜指出，隨著產業變革，公司積極延攬國際頂尖人才，並透過人才投資與公司營運目標結合，加速人才價值發揮  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E4%BA%8C%E5%BA%A6%E5%A5%AA%E7%8D%8E-%E6%8B%BF%E4%B8%8B%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95atd%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%A4%A7%E7%8D%8E-084208004.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E4%BB%A5%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0%E8%81%B7%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%86%8D%E5%A5%AAatd%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E5%AF%A6%E5%8B%99%E7%8D%8E-080200073.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[2]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0%E8%81%B7%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E5%86%8D%E5%A5%AA%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8D%93%E8%B6%8A%E5%AF%A6%E5%8B%99%E7%8D%8E-072936217.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a>。該計畫自 2020 年執行至今，已有超過百位主管參與受益，並創下高達 90% 以上的高階人才留任率  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E7%99%BC%E7%A7%91%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E9%AB%98%E9%9A%8E%E4%B8%BB%E7%AE%A1%E5%88%B0%E8%81%B7%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E7%8D%B2%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E5%8D%94%E6%9C%83%E7%8D%8E-070804037.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[4]</a>。"
