    "Title": "[AI 摘要] 台股盤中一度重挫逾千點 權值股台積電跌幅收斂",
    "Content": "台股今日開低走低，終場下跌716.26點，跌幅達1.75%，收在40,175.56點，權值股台積電 (2330) 終場下跌35元，收在2,205元，跌幅1.56%。\n\n受美股科技股走弱及國際地緣政治緊張局勢影響，台股今日盤中一度重挫逾千點，然盤中權值股跌幅收斂，終場跌點收窄。市場資金明顯從電子股撤出，轉往防禦性標的  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/1%E5%88%B02%E5%A5%88%E7%B1%B3%E5%B7%AE%E8%B7%9D-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%88%86%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%E5%89%A918%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E8%97%8F%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-070652801.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E8%99%95%E5%88%86%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%85%88%E9%80%B21-52%E5%84%84%E8%82%A1-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D244%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-133633055.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[2]</a> <a href='https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/5441575' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[3]</a>。\n\n資料來源：新聞庫 | 期間：過去 48 小時\n\n台股今日表現疲軟，受美股科技股走弱及國際地緣政治緊張局勢影響，開低走低，盤中一度重挫逾千點，然權值股台積電 (2330) 跌幅收斂，終場下跌716.26點，收在40,175.56點，跌幅1.75%。台積電終場下跌35元，收2,205元，跌幅1.56%  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/1%E5%88%B02%E5%A5%88%E7%B1%B3%E5%B7%AE%E8%B7%9D-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%88%86%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%E5%89%A918%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E8%97%8F%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-070652801.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E8%99%95%E5%88%86%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%85%88%E9%80%B21-52%E5%84%84%E8%82%A1-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D244%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-133633055.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[2]</a>。盤面賣壓集中在大型電子權值股，包括聯發科 (2454) 重挫7.21%，台達電 (2308) 與日月光投控 (3711) 跌幅亦超過5%  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/1%E5%88%B02%E5%A5%88%E7%B1%B3%E5%B7%AE%E8%B7%9D-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%88%86%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%E5%89%A918%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E8%97%8F%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-070652801.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a>。記憶體族群成為重災區，南亞科 (2408)、華邦電 (2344)、旺宏 (2337) 及群聯 (8299) 全數跌停  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/1%E5%88%B02%E5%A5%88%E7%B1%B3%E5%B7%AE%E8%B7%9D-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%88%86%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%E5%89%A918%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E8%97%8F%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-070652801.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E9%99%B3%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A6-14a%E6%99%82%E7%A8%8B%E5%B0%87%E8%BF%BD%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB-cpu-ic%E8%BC%89%E6%9D%BF%E8%B6%85%E7%BC%BA-061500990.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[4]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A9%E7%9B%A4%E9%9C%87%E7%9B%AA%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F-%E5%A4%A7%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%89%E6%BC%B2%E5%81%9C-pcb%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88-014010165.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[5]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E8%99%95%E5%88%86%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C1-52%E5%84%84%E8%82%A1-%E5%90%AB%E5%89%A9%E9%A4%98%E6%8C%81%E8%82%A1%E6%94%B9%E5%85%AC%E5%85%81%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC%E8%A1%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-%E8%A8%88%E7%B4%84632%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-%E8%A3%9C%E5%85%85-212000240.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[6]</a> <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E5%8F%B0%E7%A9%8D%E9%9B%BB%E8%99%95%E5%88%86%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%85%88%E9%80%B21-52%E5%84%84%E8%82%A1-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D244%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-133633055.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[2]</a>。市場資金明顯從位階過熱的電子股撤出，轉往防禦性標的尋求避險  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/1%E5%88%B02%E5%A5%88%E7%B1%B3%E5%B7%AE%E8%B7%9D-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%88%86%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2%E5%89%A918%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E8%97%8F%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A-070652801.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[1]</a>。金管會表示，上市櫃公司基本面依然穩健，前4月營收突破19兆元，年增31%，信用交易亦無異常變化，整戶擔保維持率近198%  <a href='https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/520%E8%A1%8C%E6%83%85%E8%AE%8A%E8%AA%BF-%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E5%86%8D%E7%A0%8D632%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E9%80%A3%E4%B8%89%E8%B3%A3-%E5%9C%9F%E6%B4%8B%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8D%E4%BD%9C%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%92%8C%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8E%E9%AB%94%E8%82%A1-102026556.html' target='_blank' style='text-decoration:none; color:#1a73e8;'>[7]</a>。"
